OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775772667
OL,3,CParents warned to speak to discuss
OL,4,Cinternet safety 'as soon as they can
OL,5,Cswipe'
OL,7,FThe independent, not-for-profit
OL,8,Forganisation Internet Matters provides
OL,9,Finformation and advice to parents and
OL,10,Fcarers to help children navigate the
OL,11,Fever-changing digital landscape.
OL,13,FContent and digital director Ghislaine
OL,14,FBombusa said: "We talk to parents a
OL,15,Flot about setting parental controls as
OL,16,Fthe first line of defence particularly.
OL,18,F"First of all, just to really make
OL,19,Fsure that you're across what they're
OL,20,Fusing and that you know what what
OL,21,Fthey're doing on you on their devices.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775772667
OL,3,CParents warned to speak to discuss
OL,4,Cinternet safety 'as soon as they can
OL,5,Cswipe'
OL,7,F"Children actually love boundaries and
OL,8,Freally want to make sure that they
OL,9,Fknow that you know how they're using
OL,10,Fit."
OL,12,FAsked what age those conversations
OL,13,Fwould be happening, she replied, "As
OL,14,Fsoon as they can pick up your device
OL,15,Fand swipe or be able to kind of
OL,16,Fnavigate a phone or even the TV remote
OL,17,Fwith the younger age group."
OL,26,@rD@DO]uD@bOU
