OL,3,CParents warned to speak to discuss
OL,4,Cinternet safety 'as soon as they can
OL,5,Cswipe'
OL,7,FWhile online gaming can be a fantastic
OL,8,Fway for children to learn, explore,
OL,9,Fand connect with friends, the
OL,10,Forganisation says parents or carers
OL,11,Fcan take a few simple steps to help
OL,12,Fyour children stay safe.
OL,14,FInternet Matters has an A-B-C guide to
OL,15,Finternet safety:
OL,17,FThe Internet Matters website offers
OL,18,Fadvice by age and activity. It also
OL,19,Ffeatures step-by-step instructions to
OL,20,Fset controls on a variety of apps.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
